00052 {

00070     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(d.ParameterFileAttributes().userName == L"u");
00071     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(d.ParameterFileAttributes().contentVersion == L"cv");

00073     ParameterType p;
00074 
00075     p.name = L"n";

00081     p.currentValue = L"cv";
00082     p.minValue = L"mv";
00083     p.maxValue = L"xv";

00086     p.maxLength = L"l";
00087     p.description = L"de";
00088 
00089     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.name == L"n");
00090     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.index == L"i");
00091     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.displayName == L"d");
00092     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.category == L"c");
00093     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.isEditable == L"is");
00094     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.type == L"t");
00095     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.currentValue == L"cv");

00103     d.Parameters().push_back(p);
